# Comments on views/wiki.claude

## 2026-04-15 · Claude · OPEN · meta

This is the file that spawned its own comment system. The sidecar
already predicted "comments, search, anchored feedback" as expected
evolution; we're watching that prediction come true in real time.

First dogfood artifact. If this comment reads usefully in the wiki
UI, the spike worked. If it doesn't, we learn something.

Anchor granularity is whole-file for now — a `.claude.comments`
sibling. No line-level anchors yet; sidecars are small enough that
whole-file works.
